{"tid":2035730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清潔香港人人有責, 大家見到非法橫額, 請善用1823 app或call 各區區議員處理","createTime":"2020-05-26T05:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T08:42:17.000Z","uid":76455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6503756a02f0679f3f9d5f1961a734f5e4c877eb","tid":2035730,"uid":76455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:51:02.000Z","msg":"大量非法橫額危害道路使用者安全<br />\n<br />\n大家見到非法橫額, 請善用1823 app或call 區議員處理<br />\n<br />\n1823 app 投訴使用方法, 1. 拍照 2. 選地點 3. 填寫具體違規情況如： <br />\nxx區 xx街 附近 發現懸掛 xx塊 未經批准非法橫額 對行人及道路使用者 構成安全威脅， 敬請立刻 處理及移除 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=gov.hk.ogcio.tellme1823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dgov.hk.ogcio.tellme1823&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYwOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=cf0a0545\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=gov.hk.ogcio.tellme1823</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/tell-me-1823/id426069047?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Ftell-me-1823%2Fid426069047%3Fl%3Den&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYwOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=0a8d3f53\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/tell-me-1823/id426069047?l=en</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oVmYw7W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoVmYw7W.jpg&h=92b020c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6fe9b69e1a4e16110bbadbad79b7a70fcd3d126","tid":2035730,"uid":49018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/weVqWGR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FweVqWGR.jpg&h=d312b18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n範例"},{"pid":"3639d7dcf10e29d46924d5bc40ef3b24fb056514","tid":2035730,"uid":76455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a9d9